about.summary: Indicators is a header-only library that introduces highly personalizible progress bars.

name: indicators
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "indicators" %}
{% set version = "1.8" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/p-ranav/indicators/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7588b10c5d877c6377a6ae7168180993ad87db72ff14a7dc359fb57c5de1976c

build:
  number: 0

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - cmake
    - make  # [unix]

test:
  commands:
    - test -d ${PREFIX}/include/indicators  # [unix]
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/include/indicators/progress_bar.hpp  # [unix]
    - if exist %LIBRARY_PREFIX%\include\indicators\progress_bar.hpp (exit 0) else (exit 1)  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/p-ranav/indicators
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Indicators is a header-only library that introduces highly personalizible progress bars.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - p-ranav
    - SylvainCorlay
    - wolfv
    - marimeireles
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
3.7.1
